<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Developments/A-Creative-Commons-guide-to-sharing-your-science" title="A Creative Commons guide to sharing your science  " alt="link">A Creative Commons guide to sharing your science  </a></h2>

	
					<p>In this online guide, Puneet Kishor of the Creative Commons explains that a more open copyright licence does exactly what researchers want, when it comes to moving research forward and receiving credit for their work. This guide introduces the Creative Commons licences best suited to science and the principles behind them. &nbsp; &nbsp;(MyScienceWork.com, 02.09.2014)</p>
